  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kingdom of Cards and Tiles</strong> is a combination of classic board games such as <strong><i>Carcassonne</i></strong> and <strong><i>Clank! A Deck-Building Adventure</i></strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263850/extras/07718300b0af02e17a6e28b7768fc5fc.avif?t=1743792503\" width=800 height=272 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine cards and artifacts in order to create varied synergies and builds. Buy new cards to Your deck and progress through the story, while uncovering hidden quests, card rewards and artifacts as you progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263850/extras/3a46131e3529ffd52cb07cba9e0b181d.avif?t=1743792503\" width=521 height=102 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The classic bard game and deck-building experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Campaign mode to complete with unique story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlockable cards and artifact.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kingdom of Cards and Tiles</strong> is a combination of classic board games such as <strong><i>Carcassonne</i></strong> and <strong><i>Clank! A Deck-Building Adventure</i></strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263850/extras/07718300b0af02e17a6e28b7768fc5fc.avif?t=1743792503\" width=800 height=272 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine cards and artifacts in order to create varied synergies and builds. Buy new cards to Your deck and progress through the story, while uncovering hidden quests, card rewards and artifacts as you progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263850/extras/3a46131e3529ffd52cb07cba9e0b181d.avif?t=1743792503\" width=521 height=102 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The classic bard game and deck-building experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Campaign mode to complete with unique story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlockable cards and artifact.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
